{
  "stem": "27285.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Which later on-- again, it is not a memory, it's only a realization-- was one side was for life-- at that time you could still die-- and the other line was it go immediately into the gas chambers, which was my sister's way to go.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And-- well, luckily we didn't know that as yet, because it's-- again, probably I would have joined her.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But it was not impossible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was such a-- it went so fast, and you didn't anyway know what you do or where you're supposed to do.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We're pushed and shoveled and whatever.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And again, it was-- it was in October, so it was quite cold.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's Poland, and we were--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know whether-- I cannot tell you that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know we went east, so east-- probably somebody told us what it is.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't tell us the name also.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in the usual way, now you go into-- being shoveled into some other place and being completely de-nuded.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, literary.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You had to put of everything, and then you were pushed into another barracks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then you were-- your head was shaven.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everything, if you had other hair, was also shaved off.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you didn't recognize your next of kin or the next person, because it so completely changed you.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you were-- you were so numb, and-- and you didn't know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So if somebody asks you, how long have you been in Auschwitz?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It doesn't matter.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It is the first impact, the first three, four days which completely turn you around and mold you into something that you don't even know that existed, or you see things that you never knew could be done to persons, to people, to human beings.",
      "word_count": 45
    }
  ],
